emporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kitchen-design-breakfast-table-030735-841-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kitchen-design-breakfast-table-030735-841-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kitchen-design-breakfast-table-030735-841-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kitchen-design-breakfast-table-030735-841-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/kitchen-design-breakfast-table-030735-841-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eClose by to the kitchen, a light-filled laundry and pantry room feels beautifully organized, with wood shelves and cabinets that keep everything calm and tidy. Thoughtful baskets and glass jars line the open storage, adding a touch of rustic charm while staying practical.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01.jpg\" alt=\"Close by to the kitchen, a light-filled laundry and pantry room feels beautifully organized, with wood shelves and cabinets that keep everything calm and tidy. Thoughtful baskets and glass jars line the open storage, adding a touch of rustic charm while staying practical.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/laundry-room-030725-841-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eConnecting the two levels, the stairs follow the slope of the terrain. Their simplicity and subtlety align with the home’s overall intent, to serve as an unobtrusive link between spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02.jpg\" alt=\"Connecting the two levels, the stairs follow the slope of the terrain. Their simplicity and subtlety align with the home’s overall intent, to serve as an unobtrusive link between spaces.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-837-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01.jpg\" alt=\"Connecting the two levels, the stairs follow the slope of the terrain. Their simplicity and subtlety align with the home’s overall intent, to serve as an unobtrusive link between spaces.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-stairs-030725-836-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bedroom is a continuation of calm with wood accents like built-in bedside tables, open shelving, and a desk, while large windows draw nature in.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01.jpg\" alt=\"The bedroom is a continuation of calm with wood accents like built-in bedside tables, open shelving, and a desk, while large windows draw nature in.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1710\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02.jpg\" alt=\"The bedroom is a continuation of calm with wood accents like built-in bedside tables, open shelving, and a desk, while large windows draw nature in.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02.jpg 1710w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02-940x1407.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02-800x1198.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02-768x1150.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02-1026x1536.jpg 1026w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-02-1368x2048.jpg 1368w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1710px) 100vw, 1710px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03.jpg\" alt=\"The bedroom is a continuation of calm with wood accents like built-in bedside tables, open shelving, and a desk, while large windows draw nature in.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bedroom-design-030725-835-03-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathroom embraces the tactile simplicity that defines the rest of the home. Soft light and natural tones define the bathroom, where creamy walls, pale wood, and smooth concrete create a grounded calm. A large window draws the outdoors in, making space for quiet, unhurried mornings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01.jpg\" alt=\"The bathroom embraces the tactile simplicity that defines the rest of the home. Soft light and natural tones define the bathroom, where creamy walls, pale wood, and smooth concrete create a grounded calm. A large window draws the outdoors in, making space for quiet, unhurried mornings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modern-bathroom-030725-839-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a look at the floor plans for the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01.jpg\" alt=\"Floor plan for a modern home built into the hillside.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02.jpg\" alt=\"Floor plan for a modern home built into the hillside.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/architectural-floor-plan-030725-834-02-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSeamlessly embedded into the Sintra landscape, this house in Galamares is a quiet triumph of student vision, architectural discipline, and deep environmental respect.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/photoshootportugal/?hl=en\"\u003eAlex Bogorodskiy\u003c/a\u003e | Architects: Vasco Lima Mayer; Sara Oom de Sousa | Engineers: Francisco Lima Mayer; Graucelsius | Landscape: PEV Arquitectura Paisagista | Construction: FLATW; Ricardo Silva Piscinas | Carpentry: J\u0026amp;J Teixeira\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
